Scripts to create and mantain the internal RPM repo for RALPH.

# Install pre-requisites:
# yum install libodb-devel

Usage:

# Copy initial specs files to rpmbuild dir
$ cp *.in ~/rpmbuild/SPECS

# Copy mock configuration files
$ copy *.cfg /etc/mock/

# Download dependencies from fedora people page
$ ./get_srpms

# Build dependendencies
$ ./build_deps

# Build ralph rpm
$ ./package_core
$ ./package_filters

# Rsync the public repo and update it
$ ./update_repo